## 🔧 Configuration

### Supabase (Optional Cloud Sync)

To enable cloud sync, update these in `index.html`:

```javascript
var SUPABASE_URL = 'https://YOUR-PROJECT.supabase.co';
var SUPABASE_KEY = 'YOUR-ANON-KEY';
```

Details: Search for `SUPABASE_URL` in index.html to find the integration points.

### Customization

**Theme Colors**
- Edit CSS custom properties (lines ~78–96 in index.html)
- `--gd`, `--em`, `--red`, `--text`, etc.

**App Name**
- Update all instances of "Peak Finance" to your app name
- Update `manifest.json` name and short_name fields

**Feature Toggles**
- Certain features (auth, sync) can be disabled in settings

## 🐛 Known Issues & Limitations

- Service Worker not yet implemented (works offline via IndexedDB, not true offline-first)
- No data encryption at rest (client-side only)
- Mobile-only optimized (desktop support functional but not primary UX target)
- CSV import limited to standard formats (Date, Merchant, Category, Amount)

## 🔒 Privacy & Security

- **No tracking** — No analytics, no ads, no cookies
- **Client-first** — All data stored locally by default
- **Optional sync** — Cloud sync is opt-in via Supabase
- **No authentication required** — Use as guest or create Supabase account

